                        <placeName corresp="INS0198QS">Qälaqǝl Maryam Ṣǝyon /QS</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1750" notAfter="1831">Zä-Mänfäs Qǝddus is the baptismal name of däğğazmač Subagadis or Säbagadis, the ruler of Tǝgray in 1822-31. The replacement of the name of the original donors by that of his name hints that the Ms. was written not later than in the early 19th century.</origDate>
